SUMMARY:THURSDAY **10 AM** Holman Lane to Pittock Mansion 
DESCRIPTION:Portland City Trail Walking Group\nAbout 5 miles out-and-back from the Holman Lane trailhead next to 3509 NW Raleigh St up to the Pittock Mansion on a lovely forested path.\n\nThere is a good amount of elevation gain (833 feet)\, but we take a moderate pace\, and we usually stop for 15 to 20 minutes at the top to take in the views and chit chat.\nOptional lunch/snacks at Elephants Deli afterwards.\nCome hang out with us!
